[Everyone's An Ally/Enemy [R1 + Up = Allies, R1 + Right = Enemies]]
author=bungholio
description=Make sure to start each stage with everyone set to allies. If you don&#039;t, you will be set to an enemy. Then you will need to set everyone to allies to attack them, and when you kill them they won&#039;t count towards your KO count.
