patch=1,EE,F0100208,extended,000001FD

[Max Defense]
author=bungholio
description=Most enemy attacks won&#039;t even interrupt you while you are doing anything. It&#039;s also infinite health since no attack is strong enough to ever make your health decrease.
patch=1,EE,C03C360B,extended,5CF5312B
patch=1,EE,C0220E86,extended,1D530E95

[RyTheHexer's Codes (Read Notes!)\Max Horse XP/Stats/Skills (SEL+R3)]
author=RyTheHexer
description=Requires my horse ENABLER code to be enabled to work! In the camp or in-game warhorse menu, enable this code. It will max the currently selected horse, then turn itself off. Repeat for others if you wish. 
patch=1,EE,D03DD79C,extended,0000FFFA
patch=1,EE,200FEFE8,extended,00000001

