[Weapon Element Type Modifier]
author=bungholio
description=This will set the element type of a weapon no matter what it already is.

These are the digits:
0 = Fire
1 = Ice
2 = Lightning
3 = No Element
patch=1,EE,91EA293E,extended,7253DF11
patch=1,EE,C09EB778,extended,062B8EC2